TEXT.Text:
{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Underground Graveyard(Lv35) - Defeat Duraman and Raty and bring back Rat tail and Rusty Armor

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Larell

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
The graveyard keeper Larell has always been alone so he is used to living on his own. But Jess and Hunter G want to become a friend with him. Larell wants to give something nice to Jess and Hunter G. Enter Underground Graveyard(Lv35) and defeat Duraman and Raty and bring back Rat tail and Rusty Armor.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Caverns - Obtain 15 Shroom Meat from Shroom

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Caverns - Ferguson

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Caverns Blacksmith Ferguson feels sorry for Sen. To calm Sen down he would like to make a warm soup for him. Enter Dangerous Cavern[Arcade mode(F1)] and defeat Shroom and bringing back 15 Shroom meat.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Cavern[Arcade Mode(F1)] - Defeat 20 Pumpkin Head

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Cavern - Ferguson

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Ferguson came to Dangerous Cavern to train in dangerous situations to sharpen his sense's. However there is something that keeps getting on his nerves. Pumpkin Head is making him laugh, and it is breaking his concentration. To help Ferguson with his training, let's go to Dangerous Cavern[Arcade Mode(F1)] and defeat 20 Pumpkin Head.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Cavern[Arcade Mode(F1)] - Defeat 50 monster

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Frank

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Weapon Merchant Frank has invested all his money into a new weapon. Frank would like to use the weapon to test it and then he can put a price on it. He thinks that in Dangerous Cavern there will be many monsters to test the new weapon on! Please enter Dangerous Cavern[Arcade Mode(F1)] and defeat 50 monsters so Frank can test the weapon safely.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Cavern[Arcade Mode(F1)]- 50 Combo

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Jess

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Jess was starting to forget all about the incident with Spark. But the incident has been told to all the other people and now he is being teased by the gang members. Enter Dangerous Cavern [Arcade Mode(F1)] and complete 50 combos.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Underground Graveyard(Lv35) - Obtain Underground Graveyard Mummy's Fresh nail from Mummy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Sofia

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village Banker Sofia wants to gain lots of money. She is planning a second job other than her bank work, let's help her out. At Underground Graveyard(Lv35) defeat Underground Graveyard Mummy and bring back 30 Fresh nails.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Underground Graveyard(Lv35) - Defeat 20 One-eyed Mummy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Sofia

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village Banker Sofia wants to gain lots of money. She is planning a second job other than bank work. She has taken a cleaning job as it has high payment. But she is finding the job too difficult. Enter Underground Graveyard(Lv35) and defeat 20 One-eyed Mummy for Sofia

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Underground Graveyard - Defeat 100 monsters from Underground Graveyard(Lv35)

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Chanpio

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Master Fighter Chanpio heard a strange rumor in town.
According to the rumor, Chanpio is actually very weak and can not face the monster at Underground Graveyard.
Now Chanpio is angry and has asked you to go to Underground Graveyard(Lv35) and defeat 100 monsters.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Cavern - Retrieve Mystery Box from Barrel Bones

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Hime

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village Him was to receive some Mystery Box from Sen at Dangerous Cavern. But when he was on his way back through Dangerous Cavern, he met Barrel Bones and his Mystery Box was stolen. Enter Dangerous Cavern and retrieve Mystery Box from Barrel Bones.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Conversation with Claire

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Claire

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
The Innkeeper Claire is looking for a picnic place for her and her children to visit. Claire want to visit the cave because children like to explore caves, but the only cave around here is the Dangerous Cavern. Visit the Dangerous Cavern and let them know how dangerous the cave is now.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Cavern[Arcade Mode(F1)] - Defeat 30 Shrooms

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Thomas

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Mercenary leader Thomas is very worried recently. Many people visit Dangerous Caverns but they are attacked by Shroom. Help Thomas by entering Dangerous Cavern[Arcade Mode(F1)] and defeat 30 Shrooms.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Cavern[Arcade Mode(F1)] - Retrieve 10 Beginners sword from Green Pong Whelp

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Frank

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Frank went to Dangerous Cavern to test his weapon. While he was testing some Green Pong Whelps appeared, he tried to fight them off but he lost to Green Pong Whelps and they took all his weapons. Enter Dangerous Cavern [Arcade Mode(F1)] and retrieve 10 Beginners sword from Green Pong Whelp

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Cavern[Arcade Mode(F1)] - Defeat Ahtoo

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Jess

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Jess managed to get back all the things that he lost at the Dangerous Cavern and he feels ok now. He also found who was behind this scheme. Enter Dangerous Cavern [Arcade Mode(F1)] and defeat Ahtoo who was behind the scheme and make Jess feel happy again.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Cavern[Arcade Mode(F1)] - Defeat 20 Mutant Spark

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Jess

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Jess was wondering around Dangerous Cavern when something bad happened. On a dark night a Mutant Spark appeared out of no where and made Jess panic and he had a small accident in his trousers. Go to Dangerous Cavern and defeat 20 Mutant Spark to get revenge for Jess

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Conversation with Larell

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Larell

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Graveyard Keeper Larell gave a present to his friends, but it seems his friends do not like the present. Larell is not sure, but he think he made a mistake. Lets encourage Larell!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Underground Graveyard(35Lv) - Defeat Bone Frag, Katler, Ratler, Kajimodo

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Share Village - Larell

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Larell wishes to make a dead soul rest in peace, but he thinks it is too difficult. Lets speak with Larell and enter the Underground Graveyard (35Lv) and defeat Bone Frag, Katler, Ratler and Kajimodo.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Conversation with Claire

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Sofia

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Banker Sofia can not sleep because she keeps thinking about Swirl who saved her. She does not understand why she is keeps thinking about Swirl and wants you to ask Claire about it. Lets talk with Claire.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Conversation with Swirl

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Swirl

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Banker Sofia met with a dangerous monster on her way back from her work. When the monster was threatening her Swirl came to help her out. So Sofia would like to send her thanks to him. Lets have conversation with Swirl.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Underground Graveyard(Lv35) - Obtain a Chamomile tablet from One-eyed Mummy

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Sofia

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Banker Sofia could not work very well as her heart is pounding and her face is flushing. Sofia wants you to get a Chamomile tablet from One-eyed Mummy at Underground Graveyard(Lv35).

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirement]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Underground Graveyard(Lv35) - Obtain a Warriors Sword from Katler

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Swirl

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
After Sofia had a Chamomile tablet she has calmed down a bit. Now that she is calm she would like to send her present. Enter Underground Graveyard(Lv35) and get a Warriors Sword and deliver it to the Swirl. The sword can be obtain from Katler.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Underground Graveyard(Lv35) - Defeat Ratler

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Thomas

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Thomas flatters himself and thinks that he's quite strong. People cannot stand his attitude anymore. Let's show Thomas that he's just a normal guy and change his attitude. To make Thomas feel that way, it seems that defeating Ratler in Underground Graveyard(Lv35) can be helpful.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Underground Graveyard(Lv35) - Obtain Kajimodo's tooth from Kajimodo

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Chanpio

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Chanpio who's already irritated by a strange rumor says that he has figured out who's been spreading the rumor.  Kajimodo from Underground Graveyard(Lv35) seems to have started the rumor, since he was beaten by Chanpio a few months ago. Let's hit Kajimodo in his face, take Kajimodo's tooth and give it to Chanpio.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Talk to Larell

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Larell

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Smith is worried about the Underground Graveyard being damaged by monsters and told the Grave keeper. Larell would know a good idea to stop the monsters. Go talk to Larell and ask him about a way to protect Underground Graveyard.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Jess, Talk to Hunter G

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Larell

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Grave keeper Larell says that he's all alone because of the atmosphere around the grave and he has a shy and quite personality. Larell says he's used to being alone but he misses people sometimes. Let's find someone who can get along well with Larell.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Underground Graveyard(Lv35) - Defeat Katler and obtain Panaceal ointment

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Chanpio

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Master Fighter Chanpio said he tripped on something while he was practicing martial arts and got injured. Chanpio injured his elbow and says he needs to get well as soon as possible. To do that, Panaceal ointment, which is well known for its special healing effect, is required. Let's get Panaceal ointment from Katler in Underground Graveyard(Lv35) and bring it to Chanpio.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Talk to Jesse

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Jesse

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Jesse in Moonlight Shore Village says that successful people have some special habits. Jesse says he has something to show you about the method to succeed, so follow his way. The very first habit to being a successful person is having a plan. Let's listen what Jesse's trying to say.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Underground Graveyard(Lv35) - Defeat 100 monsters

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Jesse

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Jesse in Moonlight Shore Village says that successful people have some special habits. Jesse mentioned that the first habit is having a plan. He's saying that the second habit is being patient. Let's learn about this patience that Jesse is trying to explain.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Underground Graveyard(Lv35) - Defeat  Bone Frag

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Jesse

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Jesse in Moonlight Shore Village says that successful people have some special habits. Jesse mentioned that the first habit is having a plan and the second habit is being patient. Let's learn about the last habit, being courageous!

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Caverns[Arcade(F1)] - Obtain 20 Jess's coin from Shroom Thief

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Jess

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Sneaky Thief Jess says he's still angry, even if he already revenged himself upon monsters in Dangerous Caverns, because those monsters took all his hidden treasures. Let's go to Dangerous Caverns [Arcade Mode(F1)] and kill Shroom Thief and bring 20 Jess's coin back.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Caverns[Arcade(F1)] - Defeat 20 Shroom Assassin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Claire

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Claire says her children cannot get close to the forest where they frequently hang out because of dangerous Shroom Assassins. Claire wants a safe place where her children can go play. Go to Dangerous Caverns[Arcade(F1)] and defeat 20 Shroom Assassin to make the place safe for children to play.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Talk to Frank

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Frank

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Equipment Merchant Frank says he should deliver the Pirate Sword that Kalygon ordered. But, Frank is worried that he might not create a good enough sword for his client because he has no idea what kind of sword would be suitable in Sea. Let's give him some hints about Kalygon's sword.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Talk to Hime

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Hime

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Frank says he promised Kalygon he would deliver a customized weapon to him. But as Frank asked Hime to deliver the weapon on the way to deliver his potions, let's ask Hime if Kalygon's sword has been delivered.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Caverns[Arcade Mode(F1)] - Reckless Obtain 20 Iron Bullet from Spark

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Caverns - Kalygon

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Kalygon says he couldn't prepare enough bullets because he was in a hurry to arrive at Dangerous Caverns to find treasure. Let's go to Dangerous Caverns[Arcade(F1)] and defeat Reckless Spark and take 20 Iron Bullets to him.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Caverns[Arcade Mode(F1)] - Achieve 100 Combo

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Caverns - Kalygon

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Kalygon says he's been training in Dangerous Caverns. Let's learn Kalygon's training method. He says he's doing a 100 Combo in Kalygon's  Dangerous Caverns[Arcade Mode(F1)] for training.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Caverns - Talk to Sen

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Dangerous Caverns - Sen

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Sen is trapped in Dangerous Caverns and is scared and worried. Let's calm him down and teach him how to escape from Dangerous Caverns.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of Winds - Talk to Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of Winds - Colin

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Magician Class Master Edelin says she has taken care of issues related with {C=0xFF016295/}Specter's Tower{C=0xFF4D0D08/}, but she wants to double check all of those. Let's go to Port of Winds and explain about the {C=0xFF016295/}Specter's Tower{C=0xFF4D0D08/} issue to Colin, on behalf of Edelin.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Collect 30 Mer Gon's Eyeball (Underground Graveyard)

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Thomas

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Thomas tells you to bring Mer Gon's Eyeball from the Underground Graveyard to test your courage. Prove your worth by collecting those eyes.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Collect 30 Zombie Leathers (Underground Graveyard)

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Thomas

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
As the second test of courage, Thomas asks you to bring Zombie Leather from the Zombies inside Underground Graveyard.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Defeat 20 Mergons, Zombies, Underground Graveyard Mummies 

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Moonlight Shore Village - Thomas

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Detail]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
As the last test, Thomas tells you to defeat all of the vicious monsters at Underground Graveyard. 
He promises he will acknowledge your courage after this mission.

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest Requirements]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/} 
Collect 30 Treasure Pocket (Kalygon Fleet)

{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Quest NPC]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Port of Winds - Crispin

